    "synopsis": "The Excommunicate Soul Drinkers answer an Ork invasion of Vanqualis, hoping to prove their loyalty to the Imperium that cast them out. Inside the chapter, a faction is ready to abandon the renegade-loyalist creed and openly embrace Chaos; outside, the Howling Griffons arrive as Imperial reinforcements who see them not as allies but as a renegade target. Sarpedon fights on three fronts at once: the Orks, his own splinter-traitors, and his fellow Astartes.",
